                            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180 text-construction">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down"></i>
                            </span>
                        </summary>
                        <div id="faq-7" class="text-gray-400 p-5 pt-0 border-t border-concrete-light/50 mt-2">
                            Com certeza! Temos uma Ã¡rea de membros exclusiva onde vocÃª pode deixar suas dÃºvidas abaixo de cada aula e nossa equipe responderÃ¡ rapidamente.
                        </div>
                    </details>

                    <details class="group bg-concrete/20 border border-concrete-light rounded-xl overflow-hidden" aria-expanded="false">
                        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-medium cursor-pointer list-none p-5 text-lg hover:bg-concrete/40 transition-colors" role="button" aria-controls="faq-8">
                            <span>Posso assistir pelo celular?</span>
                            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180 text-construction">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down"></i>
                            </span>
                        </summary>
                        <div id="faq-8" class="text-gray-400 p-5 pt-0 border-t border-concrete-light/50 mt-2">
                            Sim, a plataforma Ã© 100% responsiva e vocÃª pode assistir a todas as aulas perfeitamente pelo seu smartphone.
                        </div>
                    </details>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 9. Footer -->
    <footer class="bg-white/[0.02] backdrop-blur-2xl py-12 border-t border-white/10 relative overflow-hidden shadow-[0_-8px_32px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.3)]">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
            <div class="relative inline-block mb-6">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-construction blur-[30px] opacity-30 rounded-full"></div>
                <img src="/assets/logo-se-vira-ai.png" alt="Se Vira AI Logo" class="w-[150px] h-[150px] object-contain relative z-10 drop-shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(255,215,0,0.5)]" referrerPolicy="no-referrer" onerror="this.src='https://placehold.co/200x80/111/FFD700?text=SE+VIRA+AI'">
            </div>
            
            <!-- Redes Sociais -->
            <div class="flex justify-center gap-6 mb-8">
                <a href="https://instagram.com/exemplo" target="_blank" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-construction transition-colors text-2xl" aria-label="Instagram">
                    <i class="fa-brands fa-instagram"></i>
                </a>
                <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/exemplo" target="_blank" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-construction transition-colors text-2xl" aria-label="LinkedIn">
                    <i class="fa-brands fa-linkedin"></i>
                </a>
                <a href="https://youtube.com/c/exemplo" target="_blank" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-construction transition-colors text-2xl" aria-label="YouTube">
                    <i class="fa-brands fa-youtube"></i>
                </a>
                <a href="https://twitter.com/exemplo" target="_blank" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-construction transition-colors text-2xl" aria-label="X (Twitter)">
                    <i class="fa-brands fa-x-twitter"></i>
                </a>
                <a href="https://facebook.com/exemplo" target="_blank" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-construction transition-colors text-2xl" aria-label="Facebook">
                    <i class="fa-brands fa-facebook"></i>
